snippet.title: Palmystery
snippet.description:
A surreal horror cartoon video game by Paloma "Palgal" Dawkins about communicating with hands. 
With music by Neo Edo, Karneef/Snowboarder, YlangYlang, and Eccinaccea and a scene designed by Keith Jones.
 (Trailer music by Neo Edo)

Download the game here https://palgal.itch.io/palmystery
Please subscribe to my youtube channel and play my other games on itch.io!

Follow me on twitter for news on my games https://twitter.com/Palomadawkins

Support my Patreon!
https://www.patreon.com/user?u=425586
